<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="page--scoreboard">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/general.css"/>
    <title>Submit My Brain - TankWar Lab</title>
</head>
<body>
<nav class="nav">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="column nav__container">
            <ol class="nav__container-item">
                <li>
                    <a href="/" class="nav__logo">TankWarJudge</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/" class="nav__item">Scoreboard</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/submission" class="nav__item active">Submission</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/match" class="nav__item">Match</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/rules" class="nav__item">Rules</a>
                </li>
            </ol>
            <ol class="nav__container-item">
                <li id="signin">
                    <a href="/profile" class="nav__item"><%= realName %></a>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>
<div class="slideout-panel" id="panel">
    <div class="main">

        <div class="row" data-sticky-parent="">
            <div class="medium-9 columns">

                <div class="section">
                    <div class="section__header">
                        <h1 class="section__title">Submit New Brain</h1>
                    </div>
                    <% if (post) { %>
                        <% if (late) { %>
                            <div class="typo">
                                <blockquote class="success">
                                    Submission channel is closed
                                </blockquote>
                            </div>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <div class="typo">
                                <blockquote class="success">
                                    Submission Succeeded
                                </blockquote>
                            </div>
                        <% } %>
                    <% } %>
                    <div class="section__body typo">
                        <blockquote class="warn">
                            <ul>
                                <li class="text-red">Do not copy others' source code. All the code you submitted will be
                                    checked for plagiarism. Copycats will be submitted to the honor council if they
                                    claimed it as a progress of their academic work for certain courses (eg. VG101)!
                                </li>
                                <li>Do not share your source code with others. Similar submissions will be treated as
                                    plagiarism.
                                </li>
                                <li>Do not use alternative account to submit your code, otherwise you will be recognized
                                    as a copycat.
                                </li>
                                <li>Do not abuse our cloud execution service, such as intentionally trying to shutdown
                                    our judge machine.
                                </li>
                                <li>Your C++ program will be compiled on Linux, linking libm (so you can use math.h
                                    or cmath), but without linking pthread (so you can't use multi-threading library).
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </blockquote>
                        <p>Please paste your C++ source code of your brain in the text box below. Your code will be
                            automatically compiled with other files that are supported by TAs.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section__body">
                        <form method="post" action="/submission/submit">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="columns">
                                    <label>Source Code:</label>
                                    <textarea name="code" class="monospace textbox" autofocus="" required=""
                                              style="height: 50em"></textarea>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="medium-5 columns">
                                    <label>Environment:</label>
                                    <select class="select" name="compiler">
                                        <option value="c++98"
                                        <% if (compiler === "c++98") { %>>
                                            selected
                                            <% } %>
                                            >GNU C++ 8.3.0 (-O3
                                            -std=c++98)
                                        </option>
                                        <option value="c++11"
                                        <% if (compiler === "c++11") { %>>
                                            selected
                                            <% } %>
                                            >GNU C++ 8.3.0 (-O3
                                            -std=c++11)
                                        </option>
                                        <option value="c++14"
                                        <% if (compiler === "c++14") { %>>
                                            selected
                                            <% } %>
                                            >GNU C++ 8.3.0 (-O3
                                            -std=c++14)
                                        </option>
                                        <option value="c++17" <% if (compiler === "c++17") { %>selected
                                                <% } %>
                                        >GNU C++ 8.3.0 (-O3
                                            -std=c++17)
                                        </option>
                                    </select>
                                    <p class="help-text">
                                        You can change your default compiler in
                                        <a href="/user/settings">
                                            Settings
                                        </a>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="medium-5 columns">
                                    <nobr>
                                        <label>Send to Task 1 Judge</label>
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="judge" checked/>
                                    </nobr>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="columns">
                                    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="">
                                    <button class="primary rounded button" type="submit">Submit</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="medium-3 columns">
                <div data-sticky="medium" class="" style="">

                    <div class="side section">
                        <div class="section__header">
                            <h1 class="section__title">Current Limits</h1>
                        </div>
                        <div class="section__body typo">
                            <ul>
                                <li><p>Max judge time consumption: <span data-tooltip="36000000ms">10 hours</span> per
                                        day</p> (consumed <span data-tooltip="0ms">a few seconds</span>)
                                </li>
                                <li><p>Min interval between submissions:
                                        a minute
                                    </p></li>
                                <li><p>Max size of Source code: 1 MB</p></li>
                                <li><p>Max size of compiled exe: 1 MB</p></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="section side">
                        <div class="section__header">
                            <h1 class="section__title">Submission</h1>
                        </div>
                        <ol class="menu">
                            <li class="menu__item">
                                <a href="/submission/" class="menu__link">
                                    <span class="icon icon-flag"></span>
                                    My Submissions
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="menu__item">
                                <a href="/submission/O1" class="menu__link">
                                    <span class="icon icon-flag"></span>
                                    Task1 Submissions
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="menu__item">
                                <a href="/submission/submit" class="menu__link active">
                                    <span class="icon icon-send"></span>
                                    Submit New Brain
                                </a>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
